WebGL based Tic Tac Toe Game

This project allows the user to play Tic-Tac-Toe with another player or a Computer.
The game can also be run as computer vs computer.

Due to CORS policy in chrome, this project must be hosted on a server in order
for the texture to load.

The easiest method of hosting this project is the python simple server:

Access the project directory in a terminal window and run:
python -m SimpleHTTPServer

Unless another port is specified, the url is: http://localhost:8000/tic-tac-toe.html
